saat mendekati Ma-ha?

738
00:52:25,890 --> 00:52:26,990
Hentikan obrolan ini.

739
00:52:27,870 --> 00:52:29,020
Aku tak mau bicara lagi.

740
00:52:29,320 --> 00:52:30,380
Ryoc.

741
00:52:31,350 --> 00:52:34,780
Kau menginjak remmu sendiri,
